{
  "texts": [
    "As medical instruction-tuning data specific to developing conversational interfaces for clinical practice is highly limited, we plan to collect the required data to train a multi-turn conversational model.",
    "This will be in the framework of our upcoming Massive Online OpenValidation and Evaluation (MOOVE) initiative, where we seek community-driven continuous real-world alignment of MEDITRON to the needs of patients and expert physicians.",
    "Augmented large language modelsMultiple physicians suggested that to improve trust, MEDITRON's responses should provide appropriate citations to medical sources, such as clinical guidelines and relevant studies.",
    "Future research should augment medical LLMs with retrieval capabilities [48] and external tools [49] to allow models to access guidelines, journal articles, and other resources from authoritative medical sources and directly reference them in responses.",
    "These model augmentations should also enable retrieving resources specific to a time frame or geolocation, improving the contextual awareness of the model's responses."
  ]
}